Core Indicators
HalfTrend (HT): Used to identify major trend reversals and dynamic support/resistance levels.

Hull Suite (HMA): Used to determine market momentum and identify price convergence via channel gap analysis.

Entry Logic (Long)
When the HalfTrend indicator switches from Bearish to Bullish, an entry is triggered based on the following prioritized conditions:

Blue Arrow (Standard Entry): HT turns bullish, but Hull Suite remains red without significant convergence.

Green Arrow (Resonance Buy): HT turns bullish, and the Hull Suite is already Green (Trend confirmation).

Purple Arrow (Convergence Entry): HT turns bullish while the Hull Suite is still red, but the channel gap has narrowed for two consecutive bars (Anticipatory reversal entry).

Exit and Risk Management
Red Arrow (Standard Exit): Triggered when HalfTrend switches from Bullish to Bearish.

Orange Arrow (Resonance Sell): Triggered when HT turns bearish AND the Hull Suite is also Red (Momentum weakness confirmed).

Hard Stop Loss: A mandatory stop loss is set at 6% below the average entry price.

核心指標
HalfTrend (HT)：用於捕捉主要趨勢轉向與支撐阻力位。

Hull Suite (HMA)：用於判斷市場動能，並透過通道開口判斷價格是否正在收斂。

進場邏輯 (做多)
當 HalfTrend 指標由空轉多（發出買入訊號）時，根據 Hull Suite 的狀態分為三種進場性質：

藍色箭頭 (普通建倉)：HT 轉向多頭，但 Hull Suite 仍為紅色且未見明顯收斂。

綠色箭頭 (共振買入)：HT 轉向多頭，且 Hull Suite 已經是綠色（趨勢確認）。

紫色箭頭 (收斂進場)：HT 轉向多頭，Hull Suite 雖為紅色，但通道開口連續兩根 K 線縮小（預期反轉的左側進場）。

出場與風控
紅色箭頭 (初步平倉)：HalfTrend 由多轉空。

橘色箭頭 (共振賣出)：HT 轉向空頭，且 Hull Suite 同時為紅色（動能轉弱確認）。

硬性停損：進場後若價格下跌達成本之 6%，立即強制止損出場。
